item.title: Women in Technology Galway meetup-January 2016
item.description: Thank youto everyone who joined us on the night and a special thanks to Annieand Tracyfrom Workbench Galway for setting up the space and refreshments. BOI Workbench Galwaywas the perfect space to hold our meetup and I really appreciate the support from them. The facility is an excellent space for budding entrepreneurs, new businesses, and community events. Last Thursday, the first Women in Technology Galway meetup was held in BOI Workbench Galway.
